    "description": "Drop Foods into the Pot and Cook the Dishes!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn this exciting game, drop foods into the pot and create delicious dishes! When the necessary foods for a recipe come into contact, they attach together, and when all the required foods are combined, the dish is complete. For example, when meat, carrots, potatoes, and onions stick together, you’ll cook &quot;Nikujaga&quot; (Japanese meat and potato stew).<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAt first, you’ll start with basic recipes, and the variety of dishes you can make will be limited. However, as you successfully cook more dishes and increase your cooking level, you’ll unlock more recipes and available ingredients.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBe careful - if you fail to manage your foods and they overflow from the pot, it’s game over!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDishes:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n    30 varieties of popular Japanese dishes<br />\r\n<br />\r\nfoods:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n    23 types<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIf you ever find yourself wondering what to do with those extra foods, this game might be perfect for you!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDon’t just stick to making the same dish over and over. Challenge yourself to reduce food waste and experience both the fun of the game and the satisfaction of contributing to a good cause!",
